	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "This Tribune, an insult to whom led the Romans to make war on Falerii, is thought by Fraccaro to be a Gracchan substitution for the Tr. Mil. c. p. of 396, by Pighius and Münzer to have occasioned the war of 241, while Pais remains uncertain about the date (see Niccolini, FTP 395 where the discussions are cited)." .
